<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\float\_scalb">_scalb</sample>
    <title> _scalb</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> float_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>计算浮点数与2的若干次幂的乘积。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>double</return_val>
        <func_name>_scalb</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>double</param_type>
                <param_name>x</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>浮点数值</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>long</param_type>
                <param_name>exp</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>长整型指数</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>如果计算成功，返回浮点数与2的若干次幂的乘积。溢出时（依据x的符号），_scalb返回+/- HUGE_VAL，错误号设置为ERANGE。</para>
    </return>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>_scalb</routine_name>
            <headerfile>float.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2004,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* _scalb.cpp: This program scales argument by a power of 2.
 */

#include &lt;float.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;

int main()
{
    double x, z;
    long y;

    x = 123.456789;
    y = 16;
    z = _scalb(x, y);
    printf(&quot;_scalb(%f, %ld) = %f\n&quot;, x, y, z);

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
_scalb(123.456789, 16) = 8090864.123904
</result>



</manpage>